  "title": "MAINTENANCE ENGINEER",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Description:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Assist to plan and updating of maintenance, Permit to work clearances and sites scheduling.</li>\n  <li>To liaise with the clients and vendors on the contract costings and material costs related.</li>\n  <li>To use ERP software system to raise materials and tools for the maintenance operations.</li>\n  <li>Attend meetings with clients and vendors when in need.</li>\n  <li>Ensure maintenance schedule arrangements are timely on track.</li>\n  <li>Responsible for ensuring implementing safety measures in covering of Method of Statements.</li>\n  <li>To do quotations and follow up the quotations status.</li>\n  <li>Attend to sites with Site supervisors and workers if needed.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Requirement</strong>:</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>ITE, Diploma, Degree or equivalent.</li>\n  <li>Possess technical knowledges and basics on fire protection will be preferable.</li>\n  <li>Possess vehicle class 3 license.</li>\n</ul>",
